.IX Item "names_only => 1"
makes the method return a simple array containing the file names from
the remote directory only. For instance, these two sentences are
equivalent:
.Sp
.Vb 1
\&  my @ls1 = @{ $sftp\->ls(\*(Aq.\*(Aq, names_only => 1) };
\&
