in the same format as the \*(L"find\*(R" method.
.IX Xref "glob"
.Sp
This method tries to recover and continue under error conditions.
.Sp
The given pattern can be a \s-1UNIX\s0 style pattern (see \fIglob\fR\|(7)) or a
